 lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δια-, ἐκ-, ἐπι-σμάω</foreign>:—more freq. in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σμησάμενοι τὰς κεφαλάς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:73\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.73</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:110\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.110</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λιπαρὸν σμασαμένα πλόκαμον</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Call.\">Call.</a></author> </bibl> </cit> l.c.: abs., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κατέλιπον αὐτὴν σμωμένην ἐν τῇ πυέλῳ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg012:360\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">360</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Antiph.\">Antiph.</a></author> </bibl> l.c.—<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σμῆσαι</foreign> and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σμῆμα</foreign> are said by <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Phryn.</author> </bibl> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">228</biblScope> </bibl>) to be more <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram> </gramGrp> than <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σμῆξαι, σμῆγμα</foreign>; but <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Moer.\">Moer.</a></author> </bibl> (<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1515.tlg001:p.336\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">p.336</biblScope> </bibl> P.) cites <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῥύπτομαι, ῥύμμα</foreign> as the true <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram> </gramGrp> words. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n95466.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">wipe, wipe clean</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὴν κάρδοπον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg046:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lex.\">Lex.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3</biblScope></bibl></cit>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}